      "code": "# Maybe diacritics differ (tanween etc.). Let's search without hamza forms/diactrics\r\nimport re\r\n\r\ndef normalize_ar(text):\r\n    # remove tashkeel\r\n    text = re.sub(r'[\\u0617-\\u061A\\u064B-\\u0652\\u0670\\u06D6-\\u06ED]', '', text)\r\n    # remove tatweel\r\n    text = text.replace('ـ','')\r\n    # normalize alef/hamza forms\r\n    text = re.sub('[إأٱآا]', 'ا', text)\r\n    text = text.replace('ى','ي').replace('ؤ','و').replace('ئ','ي').replace('گی','كي')\r\n    # remove punctuation\r\n    text = re.sub(r'[^\\w\\s]', ' ', text, flags=re.UNICODE)\r\n    text = re.sub(r'\\s+', ' ', text).strip()\r\n    return text\r\n\r\nnorm_snip = normalize_ar(snippet)\r\ncands = [v for v in quran if norm_snip in normalize_ar(v['ayah_text'])]\r\nlen(cands), cands[:5]",
